Name: cSuccessMailBody
Value:
Hello Customer Name!

 

Please read the entirety of this email.

 

We have finished an automatic, preliminary auto insurance quote for you based on the information you have submitted online. 

 

We ran your quote with Farmers Insurance and Bristol West Auto Group. We have more carriers that we can quote with, so just let us know if you would like more options.

 

Here is what we have so far:

 

Farmers Auto Insurance Premium: FSIXMONTHPREM every 6 months or FPERMONTHPREM Per Month

 


 We still need to confirm the following details with you:

 

  • What Coverage Options You Would Like (Liability, Deductibles)
  • The Correct Cars We Want to Insure
  • The Correct Drivers We Want to Insure 
  • The Garaging Address
  • Driving History (Tickets, Accidents, Claims)

 

 

Although we try to get accurate quotes, given the automatic nature of our system and lack of information up front, we are bound to miss a few things with this quote.

 

We would love to schedule a time with you to go over this together and update your cars, drivers, and coverages to find a policy that is suitable for you. 

 

Disclaimer: This quote was generated automatically with the information you provided online. We have not run your auto driving history or credit details to get a final quote. Please contact us to get a finalized version of your quote so you can receive the most accurate premium and pricing.

Thank you!


The Farmers Insurance Team - Lake Nona Office
